data.title: Famous birthdays list for today, May 31, 2024 includes celebrities Clint Eastwood, Brooke Shields
data.meta_description: Clint Eastwood and Brooke Shields share a birthday today. Check out our photo slideshow of celebrities and other famous people with birthdays on May 31, 2024 and find out a fun fact about each person.
data.text:
Birthday wishes go out to Clint Eastwood, Brooke Shields and all the other celebrities with birthdays today. Check out our slideshow below to see photos of famous people turning a year older on May 31st and learn an interesting fact about each of them.

Top celebrity birthdays on May 31, 2024

Director Clint Eastwood turns 94

Fun fact: Has been nominated for both Best Director and Best Actor Oscars for one movie multiple times

Football Hall of Famer Joe Namath turns 81

Fun fact: Played his college football at Alabama

Comedian Chris Elliott turns 64

Fun fact: Most recently appeared in the film ‘Welcome to Redville’ where he played a sheriff

Actress Lea Thompson turns 63

Fun fact: Competed as a contestant during the 19th season of ‘Dancing with the Stars’

Actress Brooke Shields turns 59

Fun fact: Is distantly related to actress Glen Close

Actor Colin Farrell turns 47

Fun fact: Played Artemis Fowl’s father in the film adaptation of the novel

Actress Justine Lupe turns 35

Fun fact: Originally from Denver, CO

More celebrities with birthdays today

Singer Peter Yarrow of Peter, Paul and Mary is 86. Keyboardist Augie Meyers of the Texas Tornadoes and the Sir Douglas Quintet is 84. Actor Sharon Gless (“Cagney and Lacey”) is 81. Actor Tom Berenger is 74. Actor Gregory Harrison is 74. Actor Kyle Secor (“Homicide: Life on the Street”) is 67. Actor Roma Maffia (“Nip/Tuck,” ″Profiler”) is 66. Singer Corey Hart is 62. Rapper DMC of Run-DMC is 60. Country bassist Ed Adkins of The Derailers is 57. “The Amazing Race” host Phil Keoghan is 57. Jazz bassist Christian McBride is 52. Actor Archie Panjabi (“The Good Wife”) is 52. Actor Merle Dandridge (“Greenleaf”) is 49. Trumpet player Scott Klopfenstein of Reel Big Fish is 47. Actor Eric Christian Olsen (“NCIS: Los Angeles”) is 47. Drummer Andy Hurley of Fall Out Boy is 44. Rapper Waka Flocka Flame is 38. Actor Curtis Williams Jr. (“Parent’Hood”) is 37. Singer Normani Hamilton of Fifth Harmony is 28.
